<title>ʿạyzyn yạ rb nkwn ʿạysẖyn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ʿạyzyn yạ rb .. nkwn ʿạysẖyn ḥsb qṣdk
 ʿạyzyn .. ḥyạtnạ tkwn tʿbyr ṣḥyḥ ʿnk
 wtkwn mlạmḥnạ .. mrswmẗ ʿly̱ rsmk
 (wtlạqy fynạ kẖḍwʿ .. wtlạqy fynạ kẖsẖwʿ
 wtlạqy fynạ mḥbtk .. wtlạqy qlb yswʿ)2
 (yswʿ mlyạn bḥb ạlnạs .. wbạlạ̹ḥsạs wbạlbsmẗ
 wkẖyrh ybạn fy kl mkạn .. mʿ ạlạ̹ḥsạn wbạlnʿmẗ)2
 (wlyh slṭạn ʿly̱ ạlạ̉kwạn .. bfʿl ạlrwḥ wbạlklmẗ)2
 (slạm byzyd wʿhd jdyd .. ʿlynạ yfyḍ gẖny̱ wrḥmẗ)2</lyrics>
</song>